How to withdraw assets using the eVESTX Swap for the other chain?
1
Select the asset you want to withdraw in the field on the left.
2
Paste the address to which you want to send the assets.
3
Select a network. Make sure the platform or application you are withdrawing to supports the selected network.
4
Enter the amount you want to withdraw and the network that will be used for this. Fees are listed separately below.
Check the correctness of filling in the fields and confirm the action.
